
#to convert fasta file to 1 line-sequence file
----
perl fasta1line.pl input.fasta output.fasta
-----------------
-----------------

#to split fasta file to small sequential fasta file (require 1line-sequence fasta)
-----
usage: run_slidingSeq.py -f SEQFILE -w WINSIZE -s STEP -p PATH

WINSIZE: window size or sequence lenght
STEP: step size for moving
PATH: output path
-----------------
-----------------
